quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  31,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  31,1,alum
  31,2,yeh kitaab hakeem ki ayaat hain
  31,3,hadaayat aur rehmat naiko car logon ke liye
  31,4,"jo namaz qaim karte hain, zkoh dete hain aur akhirat par yaqeen rakhtay hain"
  31,5,yahi log apne rab ki taraf se raah e raast par hain aur yahi Falah panay walay hain
  31,6,aur insanon hi mein se koi aisa bhi hai jo kalaam dilfaraib khareed kar lata hai taakay logon ko Allah ke rasta se ilm ke baghair bhatka day aur is rastay ki dawat ko mazaq mein ura day aisay logon ke liye sakht zaleel karne wala azaab hai
  31,7,"usay jab hamari ayaat sunai jati hain to woh barray ghamand ke sath is terhan rukh phair laita hai goya ke is ne inhen suna hi nahi, goya ke is ke kaan behray hain acha, Musda suna do usay aik dard naak azaab ka"
  31,8,"Albata jo log imaan le ayen aur naik amal karen, unn ke liye Nemat bhari jannaten hain"
  31,9,jin mein woh hamesha rahen ge yeh Allah ka pukhta wada hai aur woh zabardast aur hakeem hai
  31,10,is ne asmano ko peda kya baghair satonon ke jo tum ko nazar ayen uss ne zameen mein pahar jama diye taakay woh tumhe le kar dhalak nah jaye is ne har terhan ke janwar zameen mein phela diye aur aasman se pani barsaya aur zameen mein qisam qisam ki umdah cheeze uga den
  31,11,"yeh to hai Allah ki takhleeq, ab zara mujhe dikhao, un dosaron ne kya peda kya hai? asal baat yeh hai ke yeh zalim log Sarih gumraahi mein parre hue hain"
  31,12,hum ne luqman ko hikmat ataa ki thi ke Allah ka shukar guzaar ho jo koi shukar kere uss ka shukar uss ke apne hi liye mufeed hai aur jo koi kufar kere to haqeeqat mein Allah be niaz aur aap se aap Mahmood hai
  31,13,"yaad karo jab luqman apne betay ko nasiyaat kar raha tha to is ne kaha"" beta! khuda ke sath kisi ko shareek nah karna, haq yeh hai ke shirk bohat bara zulm hai """
  31,14,"aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke hum ne ensaan ko apne walidain ka haq pehchanney ki khud takeed ki hai uss ki maa ne zeaf par zeaf uttha kar usay apne pait mein rakha aur do saal uss ka doodh chootnay mein lagey ( isi liye hum ne uss ko nasiyaat ki ke ) mera shukar kar aur apne walidain ka shukar baja laa, meri hi taraf tujhe palatna hai"
  31,15,"lekin agar woh tujh par dabao dalain ke mere sath to kisi aisay ko shareek kere jisay to nahi jaanta to un ki baat hargiz nah maan duniya mein un ke sath naik bartao karta reh magar pairwi uss shakhs ke rastay ki kar jis ne meri taraf rujoo kya hai phir tum sab ko palatna meri hi taraf hai, uss waqt mein tumhe bta dun ga ke tum kaisay amal karte rahay ho"
  31,16,"( aur luqman ne kaha tha ke )"" beta, koi cheez rai ke dana barabar bhi ho aur kisi chattaan mein ya asmano ya zameen mein kahin chhupi hui ho, Allah ussay nikaal laaye ga woh bareek been aur bakhabar hai"
  31,17,"beta, namaz qaim karne ka hukum day, badi se mana kar, aur jo museebat bhi parre is par sabr kar yeh woh baatein hain jin ki barri takeed ki gayi hai"
  31,18,"aur logon se mun phair kar baat nah kar, nah zameen mein akarr kar chal, Allah kisi khud pasand aur fakhr jatanay walay shakhs ko pasand nahi karta"
  31,19,"apni chaal mein aitdaal ikhtiyar kar, aur apni aawaz zara pust rakh, sab awazon se ziyada burii aawaz gadhon ki aawaz hoti hai"
  31,20,"kya tum log nahi dekhte ke Allah ne zameen aur asmano ki saari cheeze tumahray liye maskhar kar rakhi hain aur apni khuli aur chhupi naematain tum par tamam kar di hain? iss par haal yeh hai ke insanon mein se kuch log hain jo Allah ke baray mein jhagarte hain baghair is ke ke un ke paas koi ilm ho, ya hadaayat, ya koi roshni dikhaane wali kitaab"
  31,21,aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke pairwi karo uss cheez ki jo Allah ne nazil ki hai to kehte hain ke hum to uss cheez ki pairwi karen ge jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai kya yeh unhi ki pairwi karen ge khuwa shetan unn ko bharakti hui aag hi ki taraf kyun nah bulaataa raha ho ?
  31,22,"jo shakhs apne aap ko Allah ke hawala kar day aur amlan woh naik ho, is ne fi al waqea aik bharoosay ke qabil sahara thaam liya, aur saaray mamlaat ka aakhri faisla Allah hi ke haath hai"
  31,23,"ab jo kufar karta hai is ka kufar tumhe gham mein mubtala nah kere, inhen palat kar aana to hamari hi taraf hai, phir hum inhen bta den ge ke woh kya kuch kar ke aeye hain yaqeenan Allah seenon ke chupay hue raaz taq jaanta hai"
  31,24,"hum thori muddat inhen duniya mein mazay karne ka mauqa day rahay hain, phir un ko be bas kar ke aik sakht azaab ki taraf khech le jayen ge"
  31,25,"agar tum inn se pucho ke zameen aur asmano ko kis ne peda kya hai, to yeh zaroor kahin ge ke Allah ne kaho الحمدللہ magar un mein se aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  31,26,"asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai Allah hi ka hai, be shak Allah be niaz aur aap se aap Mahmood hai"
  31,27,zameen mein jitne darakht hain agar woh sab ke sab qalam ban jayen aur samandar ( dawaat ban jaye ) jisay saat mazeed samandar roshnaye muhayya karen tab bhi Allah ki baatein ( likhnay se ) khatam nah hon gi be shak Allah zabardast aur hakeem hai
  31,28,tum saaray insanon ko peda karna aur phir dobarah jِla uthana to ( uss ke liye ) bas aisa hai jaisay aik mutnaqas ko ( peda karna aur jِla uthana ) haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah sab kuch sُnne aur dekhnay wala hai
  31,29,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah raat ko din mein pirota howa le aata hai aur din ko raat mein? uss ne sooraj aur chaand ko maskhar kar rakha hai, sab aik waqt muqarrar taq chalay ja rahay hain, aur ( kya tum nahi jantay ) ke jo kuch bhi tum karte ho Allah uss se bakhabar hai"
  31,30,"yeh sab kuch is wajah se hai ke Allah hi haq hai aur usay chore kar jin doosri cheezon ko yeh log pukarte hain woh sab baatil hain, aur ( is wajah se ke ) Allah hi buzurag o bartar hai"
  31,31,kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke kashti samandar mein Allah ke fazl se chalti hai taakay woh tumhe apni kuch nishanain dukhaay? Dur haqeeqat is mein bohat si nishanain hain har uss shakhs ke liye jo sabr aur shukar karne wala ho
  31,32,"aur jab ( samandar mein ) inn logon par aik mouj saibanon ki terhan chhaa jati hai to yeh Allah ko pukarte hain apne deen ko bilkul isi ke liye khalis kar ke, phir jab woh bacha kar inhen khushki taq pouncha deta hai to un mein se koi iqtisad brtta hai, aur hamari nishanion ka inkaar nahi karta magar har woh shakhs jo ghddar aur nashukara hai"
  31,33,"logo, bachcho apne rab ke ghazab se aur daro uss din se jabkay koi baap apne betay ki taraf se badla nah day ga aur nah koi beta hi apne baap ki taraf se kuch badla dainay wala hoga fi al waqea Allah ka wada sacha hai pas yeh duniya ki zindagi tumhe dhokay mein nah daaley aur nah dhoka baz tum ko Allah ke muamlay mein dhoka dainay paye"
  31,34,"uss gharri ka ilm Allah hi ke paas hai, wohi barish barsata hai, wohi jaanta hai ke maaon ke paiton mein kya parwarish pa raha hai, koi mutnaqas nahi jaanta ke kal woh kya kamaai karne wala hai aur nah kisi shakhs ko yeh khabar hai ke kis sarzamen mein is ki mout aani hai, Allah hi sab kuch jan-nay wala aur bakhabar hai"
